thentication and access with different format and function, it almost impossible to create a general rule which can fit into Excel row and column.&nbsp;<br><br>Regards,<br>Fauzee<o:p></o:p></span></p></div><p class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto'><span lang=EN-US style='border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;padding:0cm'><img border=0 width=1 height=1 id="_x0000_i1029" src="cid:image005.jpg@01DBB2AC.A0034710" alt=image.png></span><span lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div><p class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto'><span lang=EN-US style='border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;padding:0cm'><img border=0 width=1 height=1 id="_x0000_i1030" src="cid:image005.jpg@01DBB2AC.A0034710" alt=image.png></span><span lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></p></div></div></div></div><p class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto'><span lang=EN-US style='border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;padding:0cm'><img border=0 width=1 height=1 id="_x0000_i1031" src="cid:image005.jpg@01DBB2AC.A0034710" alt=image.png></span><span lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></p></div></div></div></div><p class=MsoNormal><span lang=EN-US style='border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;padding:0cm'><img border=0 width=1 height=1 id="_x0000_i1032" src="cid:image008.jpg@01DBB2AC.A0080200" alt="ë³´ë¸ ì¬ëì´ ì ê±°í ì´ë¯¸ì§ìëë¤."></span><span lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></p></div></body></html>

